flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B{Removal list ready?}
    B -- No --> C[Request list of packages marked for removal]
    B -- Yes --> D[Review summary: impact + protected items]
    D --> E{Critical/protected packages present?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Require explicit override or exclude]
    E -- No --> G{Approve removal batch?}
    F --> G
    G -- No --> H[Cancel; ask for revised list]
    G -- Yes --> I[Trigger removals]
    I --> J{Completed?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Notify success; confirm cleanup]
    J -- No --> L[Notify failures; assign follow-up]
    K --> M([Done])
    L --> M

